org.deviceconnect.android.profile

クラス KeyEventProfile

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.deviceconnect.android.profile.DConnectProfile
      • org.deviceconnect.android.profile.KeyEventProfile
  • すべての実装されたインタフェース:
    DConnectProfileConstants, KeyEventProfileConstants

    public class KeyEventProfile
extends DConnectProfile
implements KeyEventProfileConstants
    Key Event Profile.

    API that provides a smart device key event operation function.
    Device plug-in that provides a button operation function by extending this class, and implements the corresponding API that.

    API provides methods

    The request to each API of Key Event Profile, following callback method group is automatically invoked.
    Subclass is to implement the functionality by overriding the method for the API provided by the device plug-in from the following methods group.
    Features that are not overridden automatically return the response as non-compliant API.

    • Key Down API [GET] : onGetOnDown(Intent, Intent, String)
    • Key Up API [GET] : onGetOnUp(Intent, Intent, String)
    • Key Down Event API [Register] : onPutOnDown(Intent, Intent, String, String)
    • Key Up Event API [Register] : onPutOnUp(Intent, Intent, String, String)
    • Key Down Event API [Unregister] : onDeleteOnDown(Intent, Intent, String, String)
    • Key Up Event API [Unregister] : onDeleteOnUp(Intent, Intent, String, String)
    作成者:
    NTT DOCOMO, INC.
